<3004><16780220>:Subdual
<3005><16780221>:Type of feat: Automatic
Prerequisite: None

You may use this feat to activate subdual mode, which will cause your PC to do non-lethal damage for purposes of subduing or knocking out an opponent without killing him/her/it.  Drag the feat icon from the character sheet down onto one of the hotbar quickslots for easy activation.  Note that non-lethal damage works against both PCs and NPCs, but does not mean the damage done by your opponent will be non-lethal.  Nonlethal attacks may not be made with ranged weapons.  Nonlethal damage heals much more quickly than normal damage, and can be restored by normal healing spells. 
